{
  "stem": "26672.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most were people, either farmers or dealing in farm goods, like grain, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they must have known the squire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he beginning, took in these people to try and save them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's-- that's-- I can assume so.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm not quite sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He obviously needed laborers as well, so he took the people in to labor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One-- one, particularly, was the wife of the rabbinate-- we call him in Hebrew-- of our rabbi's-- rabbi's wife and his daughter, [?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Ahel, ?] who was my godmother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember that I was told that she was my godmother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then the-- the mother was quite an elderly woman already by then.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But nevertheless, I mean, people had some influence with these squires, and they-- but they bribed them to take them in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We thought it was-- maybe they thought it was only going to be days or weeks before the war would be over, and they would go.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they were hiding out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would imagine happened to so many others.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's all I can assume.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there was a ghetto, obviously.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All Jews lived in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if I looked for somebody-- I can't even remember his name, even-- and I looked for-- for this cousin, a distant cousin that I have.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to look for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was in the ghetto, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like all ghettos.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some did the-- I mean, we're not talking about Warsaw ghettos.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Obviously, it was much different than all large ghettos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But these small ghettos, being in small towns, it was restricted, obviously, to go out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were restrictions of what you could do, but it wasn't threatening-- life-threatening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "People were surrounded after taken to a different works.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Like this friend of mine, Monty Tabachnik, [?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
